<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Thank You | To Have & Hold Event Decor</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,700;1,400;1,600&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --white:      #ffffff;
      --off-white:  #faf8f6;
      --rose:       #b86262;
      --rose-light: #c47575;
      --rose-pale:  #ead4d4;
      --rose-wash:  #f5eaea;
      --ink:        #1e1714;
      --ink-mid:    #4a3d38;
      --ink-soft:   #7a6b63;
      --ink-faint:  #b0a099;
      --rule:       #e0d4cc;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--ink);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 64px 24px;
    }

    /* ── LOGO SLOT ── */
    .logo-wrap {
      margin-bottom: 56px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo-wrap img {
      height: 120px;
      width: auto;
    }

    /* ── CARD ── */
    .card {
      background: var(--rose-pale);
      max-width: 720px;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 56px 64px;
      position: relative;
      border-top: 2px solid var(--rose);
      animation: fadeUp 0.75s ease both;
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    }

    .card-eyebrow {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.32em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--rose);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .card-eyebrow::before {
      content: '';
      width: 24px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--rose);
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    h1 em {
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--rose);
    }

    .rule {
      width: 36px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--rose);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: var(--ink-mid);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .card p strong {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .card p:last-of-type {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .sign-off {
      margin-top: 36px;
      padding-top: 28px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rose-light);
    }
    .sign-off p {
      margin-bottom: 4px !important;
      font-size: 14px !important;
      color: var(--ink-soft) !important;
    }
    .sign-off .brand {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 17px !important;
      font-weight: 700 !important;
      color: var(--ink) !important;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    /* ── BACK LINK ── */
    .back-link {
      margin-top: 36px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ink-faint);
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .back-link::before { content: '←'; }
    .back-link:hover { color: var(--rose); }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .card { padding: 40px 28px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- LOGO: keep your existing logo here -->
  <div class="logo-wrap">
    <img src="https://kajabi-storefronts-production.kajabi-cdn.com/kajabi-storefronts-production/file-uploads/themes/2164760737/settings_images/c21ddcd-f44b-460-3b0-5ac22861e427_586e73cf-96a0-4ec7-83b0-c6a0cffdcb0c.png" alt="To Have & Hold Event Decor" />
  </div>

  <!-- THANK YOU CARD -->
  <div class="card">
    <p class="card-eyebrow">Inquiry Received</p>
    <h1>Thank you for<br>reaching <em>out.</em></h1>
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <p>We're so honored you're considering <strong>To Have &amp; Hold Decor</strong> for your special day.</p>
    <p>Your inquiry has been received and we're reviewing the details. You can expect to hear from us within <strong>24&ndash;48 hours.</strong></p>
    <p>In the meantime, feel free to explore our work and gather inspiration. We can't wait to connect with you and bring your vision to life.</p>

    <div class="sign-off">
      <p>Warmly,</p>
      <p class="brand">To Have &amp; Hold Decor</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a href="/" class="back-link">Back to home</a>

</body>
</html>
